# Decision sheet — the right gold object

| Scenario | Pick |
|---|---|
| Heavy agg, BI refreshes hourly | **Materialized view** |
| Continuous fact ingestion | **Streaming table** |
| Wrapper / hide PII / common filter | **View** |
| Pipeline w/ quality, lineage, CDC | **Declarative Pipeline** |
| SCD 2 history from CDC | **`APPLY CHANGES ... SCD TYPE 2`** |
| Drop bad rows, keep running | **`expect or drop`** |
| Stop on critical violation | **`expect or fail`** |
| Reject at write, plain Delta | **`CHECK` constraint** |
| Custom batch you control | **Delta table + Jobs task** |
